    sage: VS = GF(2)^3
    sage: e = VS.random_element()
    sage: e.parent() is VS
    True
    sage: S = set(vector(v, immutable=True) for v in VS)
    sage: S1 = set()
    sage: while S != S1:
    ....:     S1.add(vector(VS.random_element(), immutable=True))

TESTS::

    sage: w = vector(GF(2), [-1,0,0,0])
    sage: w.set_immutable()
    sage: isinstance(hash(w), int)
    True
"""

